== Description == <!--T:13--> 

<!--T:2-->
The [[Image:Draft_Snap_Intersection.svg|24px]] '''Draft Snap Intersection''' option snaps to the intersection of two edges, and ({{Version|1.1}}) the intersection of a face and an edge. The faces and edges can belong to [[Draft_Workbench|Draft]] or [[BIM_Workbench|BIM]] objects but also to objects created with other [[Workbenches|workbenches]].

<!--T:18-->
This snap option will also find apparent intersections of (extended) straight edges if [[Image:Draft_Snap_WorkingPlane.svg|16px]] [[Draft_Snap_WorkingPlane|Draft Snap WorkingPlane]] is active as well.

